#!bin/bash

langf=$(tput bold && tput setaf 1)
langn=ruby
langv=$(ruby --version)

g=$(tput setaf 5)
b=$(tput bold)
reset=$(tput sgr0)

cat << EndOfIntro
${g}glasnt${reset}'s wat-reference for ${langf}${langn}${reset}

We're using: 
${langv}

Try these examples: 

not true && false

not true and false

See the ${b}${langn}/README.md${reset} for references, and more information. 
ðŸ’Ž
EndOfIntro
